AB  - A GLS estimator of a triangular model with covariance restrictions is proposed that is asymptotically equivalent to the optimal minimum distance estimator regardless of nonnormality. The estimator used for the error covariance matrix Σ is a matrix-weighted average of the efficient restricted and unrestricted estimators of Σ. The relative weights are determined by a measure of the departure from normality.
ER  - 
